change the color range for these apps as accurately

00:03:11.750 --> 00:03:13.040
as possible.

00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:17.799
I'm not sure if I like the limited support
for those apps listed, so I'll just keep that

00:03:17.799 --> 00:03:18.980
